EN: This rifle is the soldiers' primary weapon.

ZH: 在战场上，需要有各种各样的武器来应对不同的情况。
EN: In the battlefield, a variety of weapons are needed to handle different situations.

ZH: 他被指控持有非法武器。
EN: He was charged with possessing illegal weapons.

ZH: 部队正在巡逻，以确保非法武器不会流入城市。
EN: The troops are patrolling to ensure that illegal weapons do not flow into the city.

ZH: 孩子们不应该接触任何形式的武器。
EN: Children should not have access to any form of weapons.

ZH: 武器暴力永远不是解决问题的正确方式。
EN: Weapon violence is never the right way to solve problems.

ZH: 他们试图掩盖他们购买了大量的武器。
EN: They tried to cover up their purchase of large quantities of weapons.

ZH: 在这个国家，持有武器需要严格的许可。
EN: Holding weapons in this country requires strict permits.

ZH: 那个团体声称他们只是在为自卫而准备武器。
EN: The group claimed they were just preparing weapons for self-defense.

ZH: 爆炸的威力远远超过了普通的冷兵器武器。
EN: The power of an explosion far exceeds that of regular melee weapons.

ZH: 警方已经查封了这家商店，因为他们销售非法武器。
EN: The police have sealed off this shop as they were selling illegal weapons.

ZH: 法律严格禁止私人持有任何武器。
EN: The law strictly prohibits private individuals from holding any weapons.

ZH: 武器出现在这个小镇上，让所有人感到恐慌。
EN: The appearance of weapons in this small town has caused panic among the residents.

