EN: Fighter jets are one of the air force's important weapons.

ZH: 他使用他掌握的武器来保护自己的家人。
EN: He uses the weapons at his disposal to protect his family.

ZH: 他花费了大量金钱购买最新的武器。
EN: He spent a lot of money buying the latest weapons.

ZH: 我们应当努力限制武器的使用，以避免暴力事件。
EN: We should strive to limit the use of weapons to avoid violent incidents.
